ourney: \n\u2022 Upload and Share: Capture a spatial video with an iPhone 15 Pro/Max or newer and share it with the world through Sotial.\n\nDive into Spatial Video:\n\u2022 Seamless VR Integration: Enjoy an immersive experience by watching spatial videos on your Quest VR headset.\n\u2022 Follow and Engage: Connect with friends and creators, follow their spatial video journeys, and never miss a moment in 3D.\n\nJoin Sotial today \u2013 where your world leaps into the new dimension of social media!\n\nNotes:\n\u2022 Capturing spatial videos requires an iPhone 15 Pro/Max or newer.", "short_description": "Share and Experience the World in a New Dimension!\n\nSotial is a pioneering social media service that brings spatial video to your fingertips. From the everyday to the extraordinary, Sotial transforms your world into a captivating immersive experience."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://about.amazevr.com/privacy-notice", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.amazevr.com/termsofservice", "publisher_name": "AmazeVR", "support_website_url": "https://amazevr.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/", "website_url": "https://www.sotial.io/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "434961926215971"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7211517985577446"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "427150393046078"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "42715039304